the libyan leader has been open about his own support for some 
terrorism in 1985 when palestinians attacked airports in rome and 
vienna killing 15 people including an 11yearold american girl 
gadhafi called the incidents the most sacred action on earth 
asked about those remarks reagan said i dont answer fellows 
who think its all right to shoot 11yearold girls 
gadhafi has been at libyas helm since he overthrew king idris in 
1969 one of his first actions then was to close down us and 
