<TEXT>
london the reagan years brought a specialness to the 
britishamerican relationship not seen since world war ii and prime 
minister margaret thatcher made it the cornerstone of her foreign 
policy 
for reagan mrs thatcher has stood alone among the other west 
european leaders even at political cost for example she was the 
