more than 700 cars and trucks went on display 
wednesday at the north american automobile show and if the new 
models are any indication the cars of the 90s will have a 
decidedly windswept look 
the newly renamed detroit auto show began two days of media 
previews with the introduction of a new luxury car line from japan 
