year will range in price from about 22000 to 40000 
the cars are targeted at west german luxury performance cars made 
by bmw and mercedesbenz that often are favored by the 35 to 
54yearold buyer on the way up the financial ladder 
the first aim is the large base of japanese owners who are 
moving up in the 1990s said infiniti general manager william 
bruce 
